<br>
Valmar - Guildleader<br>
Giradella - Scribe/Webmaster<br>
Khoal - Quests/Raids<br>
Atacand - Vaultmaster<br>
Mathusis - Recruiting<br>
Ndirya - Recruiting<br>
Emanie - Merits<br>
Elbrian - Master of Ceremonies<br>
Cenadieni<br>
Trubin<br>
<br>
Would also like to welcome Kidwan back into the guild, at least for the time being.  We'll see if he can put up with my poking.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Dadijob was also in attendance.  Thanks for coming!<br>
<br>
After the meeting, we went into Mistmoore Castle to exterminate some of the foul Dark Elves.  We were on a quest to get items for our brave Paladins Valmar and Atacand.  Over the course of the night, many of the hideous creatures were slain, and Atacand collected granite from a slain gargoyle.  He is now able to advance in his quests for the prestigious Armor of Ro.  Congratulations Atacand!  All of this glory did not come without expense as Khoal, Valmar, myself, Elbrian and Allerielle died from horrible packs of ravenous elves.  Sorry to those who died, but we could not have been successful without you.  You did not die in vain!  We shall schedule another time in which to retrieve some granite for our fearless leader, Valmar.<br>
<br>
In a few more levels, we must head back into the castle to slay the cooks and retrieve their cauldrons so that our paladins may complete the quest for the breastplate of Ro.<br>
<br>
Thanks again to all of those who came last night.  See you all soon. <p><hr>
